# 📊 Iran War Oil & Gas Price Analysis (SQL Project)

## 📌 Project Overview
This project analyzes the impact of the Iran war on oil and gas prices using SQL. It includes data cleaning, trend analysis, and advanced SQL techniques like window functions.

---

## 🎯 Objectives
- Identify missing values in datasets  
- Handle NULL values using SQL  
- Detect duplicate records  
- Analyze oil & gas price trends  
- Apply advanced SQL window functions  
- Compare daily and category-based data  

---

## 📂 Dataset Used
- iran_war_gas_prices_by_state  
- iran_war_key_events_timeline  
- iran_war_oil_prices_daily_2026  

---

## 🧱 SQL Operations Performed

### 🔍 1. View Data
```sql
USE iran_war;

SELECT * FROM iran_war_gas_prices_by_state;
SELECT * FROM iran_war_key_events_timeline;
SELECT * FROM iran_war_oil_prices_daily_2026;

use iran_war
select * from iran_war_gas_prices_by_state
